25:54.819 --> 25:58.179
I'm gonna go back and...
I have work to do.

25:58.189 --> 25:59.848
Dick doesn't care
that you don't make any money.

25:59.858 --> 26:02.517
Is that what you... That's not why.

26:02.527 --> 26:05.987
I just hate swimming. I really hate it.
It's disgusting to me.

26:05.997 --> 26:08.156
My mistake was saying
I would do it to begin with.

26:08.166 --> 26:09.824
You have fun.

26:09.834 --> 26:11.834
Fine. We'll have fun.

26:16.374 --> 26:17.899
People always pee in the pool.

26:17.909 --> 26:19.868
