in their pool.

26:19.878 --> 26:22.470
I'll bet you $500 there's pee in that pool.

26:22.480 --> 26:24.573
To the end and back.
Claude, you say go.

26:24.583 --> 26:26.583
Okay. Go!

26:29.688 --> 26:31.479
-How's your dad?
-Good.

26:31.489 --> 26:34.416
He and I shared a thesis advisor
at Stanford. Did you know that?

26:34.426 --> 26:36.151
