Forget it.

29:15.186 --> 29:16.845
It's interesting.

29:16.855 --> 29:19.781
This is the first time
Dick has invited us over.

29:19.791 --> 29:21.182
Are you really friends?

29:21.192 --> 29:23.418
Well, we're neighbors.
We employ Maisy.

29:23.428 --> 29:26.788
I mean, I don't care.
I just think it's interesting.

29:26.798 --> 29:32.068
Are you excited about the talk?
I'd like to come, if it's okay.

29:32.137 --> 29:35.630
My friend Blair asked me, "What's it like
to have a celebrity as a sister?"

29:35.640 --> 29:37.699
I said I've got no problem with celebrity.

29:37.709 --> 29:41.102
