and was sort of a friend of mine.

29:41.112 --> 29:43.538
-I'm not a celebrity.
-Well, you're well-known.

29:43.548 --> 29:47.742
-To a very few people.
-Just accept the compliment.

29:47.752 --> 29:51.492
I guess I didn't realize
it was a compliment.

31:17.642 --> 31:21.976
I know a girl from a lonely street

31:22.080 --> 31:25.243
Cold as ice cream, but still as sweet

31:25.350 --> 31:28.717
