31:28.820 --> 31:32.847
Hey, I saw your guy with a different girl

31:32.957 --> 31:35.687
Looks like he's in another world

31:36.060 --> 31:38.858
Go on and hide, Sunday girl

31:39.597 --> 31:40.922
