33:19.897 --> 33:21.222
Who do we know is gay?

33:21.232 --> 33:23.324
How do I know
what gay people you know?

33:23.334 --> 33:27.562
-Alan and Toby.
-And Bruce. He's gay and Asperger's.

33:27.572 --> 33:32.567
-I don't know if Bruce is gay.
-He might be. It's very common.

33:32.577 --> 33:35.637
-Your mom's pregnant.
-No, she isn't.

33:35.847 --> 33:37.805
-She is.
