38:08.552 --> 38:12.632
-I didn't think you came home.
-Where would I be?

38:13.491 --> 38:16.017
Can't Josh and Dad come
to the wedding?

38:16.027 --> 38:18.917
I've been through this. Go to bed.

38:19.263 --> 38:21.263
Can I sleep in here?

38:21.332 --> 38:23.328
No, honey.

38:23.338 --> 38:25.969
We can put a pillow between us.

38:26.837 --> 38:30.204
Okay. Just for tonight.

38:57.268 --> 39:01.529
When you were a baby,
I wouldn't let anyone else hold you.

39:01.539 --> 39:04.684
I think that may have been a mistake.

39:04.775 --> 39:06.300
Why was it a secret?

39:06.310 --> 39:09.537
Because I didn't want you to get excited
before it was real.

39:09.547 --> 39:11.806
It's not really a baby yet.

39:11.816 --> 39:14.642
In two weeks
we can celebrate together, okay?

39:14.652 --> 39:16.692
Why did you tell Margot?

39:17.221 --> 39:20.621
