39:40.478 --> 39:43.137
-Well, it's one of those things...
-Don't say anything, okay?

39:43.147 --> 39:46.273
You know what?
Just be there for me silently.

39:46.283 --> 39:47.508
Okay.

39:47.518 --> 39:49.443
