but we couldn't find him this morning.

42:29.947 --> 42:31.472
-Oh, boy.
-Wizard!

42:31.482 --> 42:34.287
Did you tell Claude I'm pregnant?

42:34.451 --> 42:36.715
-I don't know.
-You did.

42:37.087 --> 42:39.313
-Well, I guess I said something.
-You did.

42:39.323 --> 42:40.948
You don't have to tell him everything.

42:40.958 --> 42:43.918
